Huckabee Won’t Seek Republican Presidential Candidate Nomination in 2012

-- B y   M a r k   S i l v a
-- 
2011-05-15T00:59:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-15/huckabee-won-t-seek-republican-presidential-candidate-nomination-in-2012.html
Mike Huckabee , a former Arkansas
governor who ran for president of the U.S. in 2008, said today
that he will not seek the  Republican Party ’s nomination again in
2012.  Huckabee courted a socially conservative following for
victory in his party’s premier Iowa caucuses during his first
campaign. He announced his decision not to seek the party’s 2012
nomination on his evening program on Fox News Channel.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mark Silva in Washington at 
